text: A friendly church (Methodist Church) that has English, Mandarin and Cantonese Sunday Services. It  is conveniently located at one of the exits of the Bras Brasah MRT station (Circle Line).

Friendly and vibrant church. Excellent roster of engaging pastors for Sunday sermons, with lots of invited speakers. Overall, well-run church that cares about helping people get and stay close to the Lord
Great church for new comer! Feel so welcomed at first and subsequently, I get to know the people and even more, I met my wife there. God is the Orchestrator of all beautiful things
Well, its a community when you get to know the Creator of the Universe and how He loves you. And that alone really says it allðŸ˜Œ
